| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4592 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 62978c3a-43ec-5983-aaab-f29c3bcf16c3"
